divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside our house talking with my girlfriend and I turned around towards the house and I saw a large orange light hovering 400 to 500 feet over the house. I ran inside to get my family and by the time we got out of the house the object had moved and disappeared. It reappeared South about 2-3 miles away. It was hovering over a field at about the same height. There were military jets in the area, we counted four of them. We couldn't tell what type the jets were, but we could hear them. The jets came from the West and as they came near the orange light, which was round and about as big as our house, the light disappeared. The entire incident took about 1 minute or less. Nothing appeared in the sky after the jets left the area. W took some video of the object.
